==Description==
The '''White Shard''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]] first encountered in [[Sinnoh]].

==Details==
The White Shard can be used, alongside [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}}, to purchase items at the [[Shard Trader|Shard Traders]].

==Mine Layout==
The White Shard appears in the Underground as a 3x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:WhiteShardMine.png|100px]]

==Trades==
White Shards can be used together with other [[Shards]] to purchase the following items:
