| [[File:Magmarizer.png|20px]] [[Magmarizer]] || 50 [[File:Red_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] [[Red Shard|Red Shards]] <br> 75 [[File:White_Shard_Updated.png|20px]] White Shards || 625 {{Questpoints}}
|}

For details as to where one can purchase these items, please check the [[Shard Trader]] page for more information.

==Acquisition==
White Shards can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

